quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,51,"Mulungu adati, “Inu musapembedze milungu iwiri ayi. Ndithudi Iyendi Mulungummodziyekha. Koterondiopeni Ine.”"
  16,52,Ndipo zonse zimene zili mlengalenga ndi m’dziko lapansi ndi zake ndipo Iye yekha ayenera kupembedzedwa basi. Kodi inu mudzaopa wina wake wosati Mulungu
  16,53,"Ndipo zokoma zonse zimene mumalandira zimachokera kwa Mulungu. Ndipo pamene mavuto akupezani, inu mumapempha chithandizo kwa Iye"
  16,54,"Koma Iye akakuchotserani inu mavuto, taonani! Ena mwa inu mumaphatikiza Ambuye wanu ndi mafano mukamapembedza"
  16,55,Motero iwo amakana zimene tawapatsa! Choncho basangalalani pang’ono koma posachedwapa mudzadziwa choonadi
  16,56,"Ndipo iwo amapereka gawo lina la zinthu zimene tawapatsa ku zinthu zimene iwo sazidziwa. Pali Mulungu, inu mudzafunsidwa zinthu zonse zabodza zimene mumapeka"
  16,57,Ndipo iwo amamupatsa Mulungu ana aakazi. Ayeretsedwe Ambuye ndipo Iye akhale pamwamba pa zonse zimene amaziphatikiza ndi Iye ndi zimene iwo amafuna
  16,58,"Ndipo pamene kubadwa kwa mwana wamkazi kumemezedwa kwa wina wa iwo, nkhope yake imada ndipo amadzadzidwa ndi chisoni"
  16,59,Iye amadzibisa kuti asaonane ndi anthu ake chifukwa cha nkhani yoipa imene wauzidwa. Kodi mwanayu akhale naye ndi manyazi kapena kuti akamukwirire m’nthaka? Ndithudi chiweruzo chawo ndi choipa kwambiri
  16,60,Iwo amene sakhulupirira zatsiku lachiweruzo ali ndi mbiri yoipa pamene Mulungu ali ndi mbiri yaulemerero. Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndiponso ndi Wanzeru